<concept id="concept_rph_5p5_tr">
 <title>UI Terminology</title>
 <conbody>
  <p/>
  <p>This manual uses the following terms partially adopted from the "Glossary of UI terminology" by
   Microsoft. </p>
  <p>
   <ul id="ul_udd_vkp_ps">
    <li>Dropdown menu</li>
    <li>Navigation tree</li>
    <li>Node:  an entry in a navigation tree</li>
    <li>Menu bar / menu bar entry</li>
    <li>Tab</li>
    <li>Tab section: a field within a tab that's not an input field: e.g. "select single glyphs" in
     the HTW tab.</li>
    <li>Text Input field</li>
    <li>Tool bar / tool bar entry </li>
    <li>Tooltip</li>
    <li>Window</li>
    <li>Workspace / workspace mode</li>
   </ul>
  </p>
 </conbody>
</concept>
